body.description: Specifically designed for industry, the American Safety Health Institute first aid guide provides the essential guidance required to deliver basic first aid in response to the most common workplace injuries and conditions.Magid Glove & Safety is America’s leading manufacturer, importer, and distributor of work gloves and personal protective equipment (PPE), including first aid products and protective and disposable clothing. In today's rapidly changing work environment, product demands continue to evolve, requiring safety manufacturers to grow with the challenge. MAGID stays ahead of the curve by anticipating market needs and developing innovative products. Our dedication to this and our strong work ethic are reasons why customers choose MAGID as their PPE partner.MAGID offers a full line of first aid products tailored to the rigorous requirements of industry. Choose from over one thousand first aid items, including full kits, supplies, over-the-counter medications and accessories. MAGID goes to great lengths to ensure unparalleled quality. All products, where applicable, meet or exceed the guidelines and standards set by OSHA and ANSI. Safety buyers have long enjoyed the benefit of MAGID's ultra-competitive prices, and now they can extend that savings to their first aid purchases as well.Our wide selection of wholesale safety supplies include: · Woven adhesive bandages · Burn kits · Touch free soap dispensers · Ammonia inhalant · Deodorizing spray · Plastic caps · Sun screen · Wasp and hornet killer Having the appropriate first aid products on hand at all times is extremely important in any work environment, and Magid Glove & Safety is here to ensure that your employees get the supplies they need when they need them most. From outdoor safety supplies to burn injury kits, we offer quality products that provide the proper treatment that workers deserve while on the job. We also have the emergency response equipment needed to deal with time sensitive hazards or injuries.
